	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=67729><span id= >Emajica</span></a><br><span id=notbold>17 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>This robe far better than gossamer. All the gossamer robe has going for it is 2 more ac and summon efficency I. This robe give +3 int and +10 mana, all of which is alot more useful than 2 ac. I'm just glad they finally gave a robe young casters can use. For a while there you went from sr apprentice robe to flowing black or robe of oracle if you were lucky to get a deal. This should bridge a the gap and give much needed stat increases to low lvl casters. Plus, all the other pieces to the newbie quests add up! This will make leveling easier and you're mana pools will be much harder to drain.</p>&nbsp;<br>Mithander Greyhaven<br>-----------------<br></td></tr>
